Package edu.monash.fit2099.game.interfaces

This module is about the interfaces within the edu.monash.fit2099.game.

This module keeps track of the different interfaces that other classes can implement within the edu.monash.fit2099.game. These interfaces develop is-a relationships from classes that implement it. Note that a class can implement multiple of these interfaces.

Since:
1.0.0
  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    Behaviour
    Interface for classes that are behaviours.
    ConsumableItem
    Interface for Consumable items
    FadeableItem
    Interface for Fadeable items
    HigherGround
    This interface handles the interaction player has with higher grounds in the map of the edu.monash.fit2099.game
    Resettable
    Interface for Resettable items
    Tradeable
    Interface for Tradeable items
